replyContent: Sorry. The Q&A comment are still there for Health Concerns. The problem may be your text size is increased, it will move the Q&A icon off the screen to right. Please reduce text size. (Also delete/reinstall app after reducing text for this to take effect.) This will be corrected in the next release. Contact us at info@eoebooks.com for more help.
